                                      .::.        
         `---`                    -ohmNhohy+.     
      `/shyohds-                 -NmNy-  .syso.   
    `+ysys` `smm+                 ./.     `+ssy-  
   :hhss/`    :o.                          `.+yh+ 
 -hmddyo++///:-..`              `.:/+osyhmmNNNNdN/
 :myNNyo+++++++osyhddyso+//+sydmhs++:-.``````+NNd.
  :NM/              .hNNNNNNNN/`              dN` 
   oM:               +Mm.  +Mm`               ds  
   `mo              `dN/    sMs              :m`  
    :m-            `yN/      +Ny`           -d-   
     -ys/-``  ``.:ods.        `ohs:-.-:/+sys/`    
